Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.66,0:00:09.13,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi... Nishimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:12.38,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You're back at the head of the class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:15.88,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried with your grades \Ndropping there for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:17.95,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like you've \Nstraightened out your act.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.82,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because entrance \Nexams are looming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:26.05,Main Dialog,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,...or maybe it's thanks to the disappearance \Nof that impediment to your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:45.47,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:54.91,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought they'd agree to open up \Nthe roof, but they went right for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.36,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a third-year thug was \Nmonopolizing the key up 'til now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:05.84,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! Richie-boy! I'm playing \Nvolleyball with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:07.25,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How about joining in?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:11.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No. I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.54,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Richie-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.83,0:01:21.98,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're lonely without Kawabuchi-kun, \Nbut you've got to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:25.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.16,0:02:26.64,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mukae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.57,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're looking for Nishimi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:30.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.14,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.14,0:02:39.76,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I love milkshakes when it \Nstarts getting cold outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:45.43,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ritsuko-san? Are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:46.47,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:51.30,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be you're worried about \NKawabuchi-kun after he disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:54.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, there's that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.30,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It's Nishimi-san, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:03:01.19,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Like, you haven't been able to talk \Nat all or go home together recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:05.26,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, you can't just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:07.21,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,You need to make things happen yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:10.21,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.69,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Nishimi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.13,0:03:19.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Were you eating sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've got whipped cream on your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:31.33,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Kaoru-san... You're not coming \Nto the basement today, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:37.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,With entrance exams coming up, I've \Ndecided not to go for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.40,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.27,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Pops that I'm sorry \Nfor not being able to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:44.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:45.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:50.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, um... Why not study at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:58.95,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The shop's closed today? Where's your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.51,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He's off buying up stock, \Nso it's just me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:08.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a second. I'll clean up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:20.00,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,That one's my favorite photo. \NI always have it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:24.70,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you look so happy in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Sentaro's face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:34.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we get started? \NEnglish and Math, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.76,0:04:43.08,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So first of all, the word order is reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:47.72,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This "so" comes before, and the \Nsubject and verb change places.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.15,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm sorry about before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:05:01.78,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking about how you felt \Nwhen I showed you that photo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:07.28,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Since Sentaro left, you're the one \Nit's hit the hardest, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.86,0:05:10.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:14.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He may not be around, but \NI've still got you, Ri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.92,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Kaoru-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:42.74,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.36,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-san, w-wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can be alone with you whenever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:55.25,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:02.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,How...? How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're happy that Sentaro is gone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.60,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're joking, I don't \Nwant to hear such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:44.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, I haven't been \Nable to say this before...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.51,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm going to a college in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:08.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The lowest of the low!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:13.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why did things turn out like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.79,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East High Graduation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:32.25,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't call Kawabuchi-kun's name, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:36.77,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference? Everyone's \Ngoing their own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:40.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all forget being here in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:43.30,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Nishimi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:49.57,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever forget you two's performance \Nat the school festival last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:52.28,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:59.37,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,Maruo-san? Could I have the \Nsecond button on your jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:03.67,Main Dialog,Maruo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, if you'd be satisfied with mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.48,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.91,Main Dialog,Tokie,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure if I'd be able to ask you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.98,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was crying my eyes out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:13.01,Main Dialog,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:21.50,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell and good riddance \Nto this damned slope!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.74,Main Dialog,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go trudging up the \Nthing tomorrow out of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.80,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.91,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going off to a college \Nin Tokyo too, huh, Richie-rich?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:57.56,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it'll probably get a \Nlittle lonely around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.18,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, we can't get gloomy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:02.56,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's great news, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:06.82,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Ritsuko was \Naccepted at the college here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.68,0:09:10.57,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ritsuko! Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.23,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Richie-rich got into college! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.83,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan! You can stay \Nthere, but just listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.61,0:09:31.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You may not want to hear anything \Nfrom me, but just let me say this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:37.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I started coming here is \Nbecause I wanted to see your smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:42.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan, your smile always encouraged \Nme, even when things were rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:48.35,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew that feeling \Nbefore meeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:54.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ri-chan. Meeting \Nyou was a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:12.50,Main Dialog,Aunt,0000,0000,0000,,Call us as soon as you get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.40,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.13,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun, write me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.90,Main Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thank you for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:23.09,Main Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The sleeper express train, Sakura, \Nwill depart for Tokyo on track one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:25.54,Main Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Its next stop will be Haiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.86,Main Dialog,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All passengers, please get on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.15,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.98,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.42,0:10:32.69,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a little going-away gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:35.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.66,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is Ri-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:44.66,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. But there's a lunch in \Nthere that Ritsuko made for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.17,0:10:49.68,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.17,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I will. You too, Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:53.82,Main Dialog,Mariko,0000,0000,0000,,See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.33,0:11:09.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.83,0:12:02.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When you're sick, you're apt to lose heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.04,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but like they say, sickness and \Nhealth start with the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:10.61,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you have a good head on your \Nshoulders for someone so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:13.53,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no... I'm still a rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:16.30,Main Dialog,Nurse,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Nishimi, we've got an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:18.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.20,0:12:45.40,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there's a free bed in the nap room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:47.83,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get a little rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:51.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I lie down now, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:54.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:59.34,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, being a resident on the night shift \Nis even harder than I heard it'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.56,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,It takes a lot of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:02.81,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:09.47,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Our guest is a popular star \Nwho both sings and acts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:12.24,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuoka Seiji-san joins \Nus in the studio today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! I'm Matsuoka Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:16.23,Caption Top,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Guest: Matsuoka Seiji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.15,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I want to start right off with a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:21.41,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Which do you like better, singing or acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:20.38,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:21.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:23.75,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I like them both...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:24.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,...a classmate from high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:27.96,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My little sister \Ngoes nuts over that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.76,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And I like jazz, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.76,Main Dialog,Co-worker,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get me an autograph!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.58,Main Dialog,Host,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oh, jazz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:41.01,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Matsuoka's dream came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.41,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.68,0:13:53.82,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.94,0:13:57.81,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru-kun?! Kaoru-kun, is that you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika... san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:04.40,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful! You've become a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:05.33,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:12.04,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm six months along. Junichi-san \Nwants a girl, but I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.20,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I think he'd spoil her rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:18.45,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,How are you? Have you been good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.83,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.96,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:26.72,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd heard that Sentaro had taken off, \Nbut you've never seen him since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.47,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.96,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be catching up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:38.14,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've been \Ncarrying around to show everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:41.81,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,A friend from back home sent me this photo,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:45.31,Main Dialog,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but don't you think the person on the \Nfar left looks like someone we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.11,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow this photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.08,0:15:06.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:14.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've been trying to forget him all this \Ntime, but my heart is beating fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:19.09,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can stop \Nthis rhythm in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:23.11,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,If you want the church, it's \Nat the top of the slope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:26.17,Main Dialog,Sailor,0000,0000,0000,,Young priest? Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.37,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,The priest here has been \Naround for years and years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:35.38,Main Dialog,Farmer,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I think he helps raise the \Norphans from around the prefecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.62,0:15:37.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He raises children?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:41.24,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you mean the priest-in-training.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.24,0:15:45.03,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Though I hear he does nothing but \Ncause trouble for the poor priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:52.49,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.90,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:24.82,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't see this every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:34.96,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:37.25,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Pick me up, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:42.69,Main Dialog,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:59.46,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought this day \Nmight come sometime...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:40.11,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! What do you two think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:45.48,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that you can only play on special \Noccasions, but again, you do as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.53,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! Run, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait! Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.09,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:59.58,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I forget what I was like before I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.99,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind caresses my cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:06.32,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,♪Lullaby of Birdland♪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.32,0:20:10.89,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kick my heels going down the slope
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.31,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,As my worthless shadow grows　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:19.42,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an endless summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:25.12,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like sneakin' into the swimming pool
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:31.18,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's swim with our clothes on, jump in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:33.85,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A shocking seductive spiral
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:38.35,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This beat that pierces my heart is strange　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:41.76,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(It flares up, then vanishes)　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.76,Caption Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs20\b1\shad0}It's been a long time. How are you? I'm writing now because\N there's something I want to tell you, Ritsuko-chan. \NA friend of mine from back home got married at a church, \Nand in a photo of the ceremony that she sent me, there's a priest\N who resembles Sentaro-san. I'm not sure of it,\N but thought it would be worth looking into.\N The church is on a small island, so it should be easy to find. \NI just wrote this postcard to let you know. \NIf you find anything out, please write back.\N\NYours truly,\NYukari Fukahori
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:43.95,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Every miserable day is swell,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:44.89,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,dress it up
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:48.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-speed swing surrounds us
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:52.46,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,(What's this dance called? I can't stop)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:56.54,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you go, it's twined around my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:01.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,and won't leave me ever again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.00,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,This melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,...is like love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.64,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for you on that slope　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.56,0:21:36.92,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,For our after school promise　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:41.91,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a 'goodbye' blurred far away　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:56.22,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so weak, so awkward, and so fragile back then
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:03.77,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,But you gave me a small pair of wings　         　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:09.83,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,In the twilight hour of the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:15.48,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm searching for a gleam of light　　　　　　　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.48,0:22:23.45,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I could have said that I love you…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.72,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,The note that I wrote in the corner of my textbook
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.61,0:22:48.80,Songs,,0000,0000,0000,,has never been delivered to this day
